\[\ c(x,y){\pi }_2(x,y)\equiv y{c_1(x)\left(x-b\right)}^{2^m-1}+(1-y)(1-x^{2^m-1})\in {\Omega }^{3e}_{2,2^m},\] 
from which it follows that 
\begin{equation}\label{eq40}
